ABSTRACT
Implementations generally relate to face template balancing.
In some implementations, a method includes generating face
templates corresponding to respective images. The method
also includes matching the images to a user based on the face
templates. The method also includes receiving a determina-
tion that one or more matched images are mismatched
images. The method also includes flagging one or more face
templates corresponding to the one or more mismatched
images as negative face templates.
